f%20flooding%20in%20these%20undocumented%20immigrants%20brings%20the%20border%20to%20New%20York%20City%2C%20Chicago%2C%20Detroit%2C%20and%20Atlanta.%20It%20brings%20the%20border%20everywhere%20because%20we%20are%20not%20vetting%20these%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20an%20old-school%20Reagan%20fan%2C%20and%20Nikki%20Haley%20is%20a%20genuine%20Republican.%20She%20understands%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-vote-ukraine-top-issue-2024-candidate-guide%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimportance%20of%20Ukraine%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20understands%20the%20importance%20of%20how%20we%20project%20our%20foreign%20policy.%20An%2C%20if%20you%20think%20about%20it%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20crossover%20there%20that%20the%20current%20administration%20is%20trying%20to%20do.%20Trump%20being%20elected%20would%20be%20a%20disaster%20for%20Ukraine.%20Forty-six%20Republicans%20voted%20against%20funding%20NATO%20%E2%80%94%20that%20scares%20the%20devil%20out%20of%20me.%20It's%20like%20no%20one%20is%20paying%20attention%20to%20the%20things%20that%20are%20really%20important.%20We%20want%20democracy%2C%20we%20want%20liberty%2C%20and%20we%20want%20freedom%20to%20flourish%2C%20because%20that's%20what%20true%20American%20values%20are.%20We%20don't%20want%20to%20send%20American%20troops%20to%20fight%20over%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b0e0f861-0110-48db-b7be-0d6a1630b0c5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EServing%20in%20the%20military%20had%20a%20profound%20effect%20on%20my%20life.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20met%20my%20wife%20during%20my%20first%20tour%20in%20Korea.%20We've%20been%20married%2035%20years%20now.%20The%20military%20is%20a%20microcosm%20of%20our%20society%20as%20a%20whole.%20Growing%20up%20in%20rural%20South%20Carolina%2C%20I%20learned%20a%20lot%20about%20people%20by%20working%20beside%20them.%20It%20gets%20you%20away%20from%20a%20myotic%20way%20of%20thinking.%20One%20of%20my%20assignments%20took%20me%20to%20the%20DMZ.%20You%20come%20face-to-face%20with%20North%20Korea.%20You%20see%20them%20living%20in%20the%20past.%20They%20come%20out%20in%20these%20old%20woolen%20Soviet%20uniforms.%20It's%20very%20stark%20there.%20You%20sort%20of%20understand%20the%20dangers%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Russia%20invaded%20Ukraine%2C%20it%20got%20me.%20You%20look%20on%20a%20map%2C%20you%20can%20tell%20what%20the%20stakes%20are.%20There's%20nothing%20good%20coming%20from%20Russian%20aggression.%20And%20so%20that's%20what%20drew%20me%20into%20being%20involved%2C%20adding%20my%20voice%20and%20perspective%20to%20the%20mix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20response%20to%20Roger's%20comments%2C%20Trump%20spokesperson%20Steven%20Cheung%20sent%20the%20following%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%3A%20%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20dominated%20the%20primary%20in%20record-breaking%20fashion%20and%20it%20wasn't%20even%20close.%20Voters%20know%20that%20President%20Trump%20is%20the%20only%20person%20who%20will%20beat%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20take%20back%20the%20White%20House.%20It%20was%20revealed%20that%20investigators%20in%20that%20case%20likely%20engaged%20in%20evidence%20tampering%20and%20mishandling%20of%20those%20documents%2C%20which%20is%20why%20a%20filing%20was%20made%20earlier%20this%20week%20to%20dismiss%20the%20case.%20Joe%20Biden%20being%20elected%20again%20would%20be%20a%20disaster%20for%20America.%20President%20Trump%20will%20put%20America%20First%20instead%20of%20getting%20into%20more%20wars%20and%20more%20conflict%20like%20Biden%20has%20done.%26quot%3B%20(Editor's%20note%3A%20Special%20counsel%20Jack%20Smith's%20team%20has%20said%20the%20order%20of%20documents%20taken%20from%20Mar-a-Lago%20during%20the%20classified%20documents%20probe%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F05%2F03%2Fmar-a-lago-trump-classified-documents-00156124%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emay%20have%20shifted%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20from%20when%20FBI%20agents