0water%20and%20my%20plants%20are%20thirsty%2C%20it'll%20do%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20chose%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20chose%20the%20best%20watering%20cans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20watering%20can%20waters%20plants%20indoors%20on%20a%20shelf%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666b4b43ed9a404d829d9bcf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20long-stem%20design%20is%20useful%20for%20reaching%20into%20tighter%20spaces%2C%20especially%20when%20watering%20indoor%20or%20hanging%20plants.%3Cp%3ESteph%20Coelho%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20consulted%20Joan%20Mazat%2C%20cut%20flower%20business%20manager%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ballseed.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBall%20Seed%20Company%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20how%20to%20shop%20for%20a%20watering%20can.%20Mazat%20has%20been%20with%20Ball%20Horticultural%20Company%20for%20over%20two%20decades%20and%20is%20an%20expert%20in%20fresh%20flowers%2C%20container%20gardening%2C%20and%20garden%20market%20trends.%20We%20also%20asked%20Mazat%20about%20materials%20and%20features%20to%20look%20for%2C%20and%20her%20favorite%20watering%20can%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EI've%20also%20been%20gardening%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20and%20have%20firsthand%20experience%20with%20many%20gardening%20products.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20combined%20expert%20insights%20with%20our%20own%20research%20and%20gardening%20expertise%20to%20bring%20you%20our%20top%20picks%20for%20the%20best%20watering%20cans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatering%20Can%20FAQs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%