nnual-meeting-quotes-valuation-trump-optimus-aws-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BS%20Yediyurappa%20Can't%20Be%20Arrested%20In%20Sex%20Abuse%20Case%20Till%20Next%20Hearing%3A%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20BS%20Yediyurappa%2C%20accused%20of%20sex%20harassment%20of%20a%20minor%2C%20cannot%20be%20arrested%20until%20the%20next%20hearing%20in%20the%20case%20on%20June%2017%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20ruled%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20non-bailable%20warrant%20was%20issued%20against%20Mr%20Yediyurappa%2C%2081%2C%20on%20Thursday%20under%20the%20stringent%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offenses%20(POCSO)%20Act.%20The%20former%20Chief%20Minister's%20son%20BY%20Raghvendra%20has%20asserted%20that%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20truth%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20Mr%20Yediyurappa%20has%20been%20charged%20under%20the%20POCSO%20Act%20and%20Section%20354%20A%20(Sexual%20harassment)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20from%20the%20mother%20of%20a%2017-year-old%20girl%20on%20March%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mother%20alleges%20that%20Mr%20Yediyurappa%20sexually%20assaulted%20her%20daughter%20during%20a%20meeting%20on%20February%202%20this%20year%2C%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Dollars%20Colony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20placed%20it%20on%20record%2C%20she%20(the%20mother)%20is%20in%20the%20habit%20of%20filing%20cases.%20I%20have%20given%20details.%20Blackmailing%20is%20her%20avocation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sandeep%20Patil%2C%20Mr%20Yediyurappa's%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2054-year-old%20woman%20who%20had%20filed%20the%20complaint%20against%20Mr%20Yediyurappa%20died%20of%20lung%20cancer%20at%20a%20private%20hospital%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20action%20seems%20to%20be%20suspicious%2C%20a%20malafide%20one.%20A%20poli