0by%20law%20firm%20Lewis%20Silkin%2C%20notes%20that%20while%20no%20formal%20complaints%20were%20made%20against%20Brand%20during%20the%20production%20of%20%E2%80%9CBig%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Ellise%20Shafer%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Frussell-brand-allegations-endemol-tolerated-not-adequately-addressed-banijay-1236037882%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Frussell-brand-allegations-endemol-tolerated-not-adequately-addressed-banijay-1236037882%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Frussell-brand-allegations-endemol-tolerated-not-adequately-addressed-banijay-1236037882%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Meets%20Zelensky%2C%20Macron%20At%20G7%2C%20Will%20Hold%20Talks%20With%20Pope%2C%20Meloni%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20summit%20is%20being%20held%20at%20the%20luxurious%20Borgo%20Egnazia%20resort%20in%20Italy's%20Apulia%20region.%20India%20has%20been%20invited%20to%20the%20G7%20Summit%20as%20an%20Outreach%20country%20and%20this%20is%20PM%20Modi's%20first%20overseas%20visit%20since%20he%20took%20oath%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20the%20third%20straight%20term.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20held%20bilateral%20meetings%20with%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%2C%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20and%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak.%20He%20will%20hold%20talks%20with%20several%20other%20leaders%2C%20including%20the%20Pope%20and%20Italian%20PM%20Giorgia%20Meloni.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%20with%20Mr%20Zelenskyy%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said%20it%20was%20a%20productive%20one%20and%20that%20India%20is%C2%A0eager%20to%20further%20cement%20bilateral%20relations%20with%20Ukraine.%20On%20the%20war%20with%20Russia%2C%C2%A0the%20PM%20reiterated%20that%20India%20believes%20in%20a%20human-centric%20approach%20and%20that%20the%20way%20to%20peace%20is%20through%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGiving%20details%20of%20the%20PM's%20meeting%20with%20Mr%20Macron%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20Spokesperson%C2%A0Randhir%20Jaiswal%20posted%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BTaking%20Strategic%20Partnership%20to%20new%20levels!%20PM%20%40narendramodi%20met%20President%20%40EmmanuelMacron%20of%20France%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%2050th%20G7%20Summit%20in%20Apulia%2C%20Italy%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20two%20leaders%20discussed%20ways%20to%20further%20strengthen%20the%20partnership%20including%20in%20areas%20of%20defence%2C%20nuclear%2C%20space%2C%20education%2C%20climate%20action%2C%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%2C%20critical%20technologies%2C%20connectivity%20and%20culture.%20They%20also%20exchanged%20views%20on%20key%20global%20and%20regional%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDay%20one%20of%20the%20summit%20was%20dominated%20by%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20as%20the%20leaders%20agreed%20on%20a%20US%20proposal%20to%20back%20a%20%24%2050-billion%20loan%20to%20Kyiv%20utilising%20frozen%20Russian%20assets%2C%20described%20by%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20outcome%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20strong%20message%20to%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20his%20departure%20statement%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bglad%26quot%3B%20that%20his%20first%20foreign%20visit%20in%20his%20third%20term%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20to%20Italy%20for%20the%20G7%20Summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BI%20warmly%20recall%20my%20visit%20to%20Italy%20for%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%202021.%20Prime%20Minister%20Meloni's%20two%20visits%20to%20India%20last%20year%20were%20instrumental%20in%20infusing%20momentum%20and%20depth%20in%20our%20bilateral%20agenda.%20We%20remain%20committed%20to%20consolidate%20the%20India-Italy%20strategic%20partnership%2C%20and%20bolster%20cooperation%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20and%20the%20Mediterranean%20regions%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20her%20opening%20address%20at%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20G7%20leaders%2C%20Ms%20Meloni%20said%20southern%20Italy%20was%20chosen%20as%20the%20venue%20to%20send%20a%20strong%20message%20to%20the%20Global%20South.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20no%20coincidence%20that%20we%20are%20hosting%20the%20summit%20in%20Apulia.%20We%20did%20this%20because%20Apulia%20is%20a%20region%20of%20southern%20Italy%20and%20the%20message%20we%20want%20to%20launch%20is%20that%20the%20G7%2C%20under%20the%20Italian%20presidency%2C%20wishes%20to%20strengthen%20its%20dialogue%20with%20the%20nations%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EItaly%20is%20India's%20fourth-largest%20trading%20partner%20in%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20with%20bilateral%20trade%20worth%20%2415%20billion.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718366460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fem8552ng_pm-modi-zelensky-_650x400_14_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-meets-macron-rishi-sunak-at-g7-will-hold-talks-with-pope-meloni-5889009%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20in%20Italy%20for%20the%20G7%20Summit%2C%20where%20he%20is%20holding%20a%20series%20of%20key%20bilateral%20meetings%20with%20world%20leaders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-meets-macron-rishi-sunak-at-g7-will-hold-talks-with-pope-meloni-5889009%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20is%20dangling%20tax%20cuts%20and%20less%20red%20tape%20to%20win%20over%20top%20CEOs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22trump%20smug%20