y%20campaigners%20raised%20red%20flags%20about%20some%20of%20Recall's%20screenshot%20capabilities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20and%20Adobe%20have%20also%20rolled%20back%20some%20of%20their%20big%20AI%20releases%20following%20backlash.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20race%20to%20do%20more%20with%20AI%2C%20Big%20Tech%20has%20been%20moving%20fast%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20rolling%20back%20big%20moves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20became%20the%20latest%20to%20scale%20back%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20feature%20within%20one%20month%20of%20announcing%20it%2C%20following%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Microsoft%20said%20it%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.windows.com%2Fwindowsexperience%2F2024%2F06%2F07%2Fupdate-on-the-recall-preview-feature-for-copilot-pcs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithdraw%20an%20AI%20tool%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20its%20new%20line%20of%20computers%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-computers-copilot-plus-pc-surface-pro-laptop-price-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECopilot%2B%20PCs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20feature%20will%20now%20only%20be%20accessible%20to%20a%20small%20group%20of%20people%20who%20are%20part%20of%20its%20Windows%20Insider%20Program%20instead%20of%20being%20broadly%20available%20for%20Copilot%2B%20PC%20users%20on%20June%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20feature%20is%20called%20Recall%20and%20acts%20like%20the%20computer's%20%26quot%3Bphotographic%20memory%26quot%3B%E2%80%94it%20can%20take%20screenshots%20of%20everything%20the%20user%20looks%20at%20on%20their%20PC%20and%20help%20them%20quickly%20find%20where%20they%20stored%20something%20from%20a%20conversational%20prompt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20privacy%20campaigners%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-copilot-pcs-privacy-nightmare-ai-laptops-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%20the%20alarm%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20Microsoft's%20Recall%20f