%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20those%20who%20had%20no%20faith%20in%20Ram%20were%20stopped%20at%20234%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSee%20the%20'Vidhan'%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20in%20democracy%3B%20those%20who%20did%20'Bhakti'%20of%20Ram%2C%20but%20gradually%20turned%20arrogant%2C%20emerged%20as%20the%20biggest%20party%2C%20however%2C%20the%20vote%20and%20the%20power%20that%20they%20should%20have%20been%20given%20was%20stopped%20by%20God%20due%20to%20arrogance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20none%20amongst%20those%20who%20opposed%20Ram%20were%20given%20power.%20All%20of%20them%20together%20were%20made%20number%20two%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20follows%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat's%20statement%20a%20few%20days%20ago.%20Mr%20Bhagwat%20said%20that%20a%20true%20'sevak'%20should%20serve%20people%20without%20arrogance%20and%20maintain%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20pray%20to%20Ram%20should%20be%20humble...%20Lord%20Ram%20does%20not%20discriminate%20and%20does%20not%20punish.%20Ram%20delivers%20justice%20to%20everyone.%20He%20gives%20and%20continues%20giving%20to%20all.%20Lord%20Ram%20was%20always%20just%20and%20will%20remain%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718359620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fimn43fvo_rss-leader-indresh-kumar-ians_625x300_14_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthose-against-lord-ram-came-2nd-arrogant-stopped-at-241-senior-rss-leader-5887895%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20ideologue%20Indresh%20Kumar%20has%20said%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%2