%20Swamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thoogudeepa%20had%20allegedly%20planted%20three%20men%20to%20take%20the%20blame%20for%20the%20murder%2C%20but%20during%20interrogation%2C%20they%20were%20exposed%2C%20the%20police%20have%20said%2C%20adding%20he%20offered%20the%20three%20Rs%205%20lakh%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20heinous%20crime.%20He%20(Darshan%20Thoogudeepa)%20has%20to%20face%20the%20consequences...%20there%20will%20be%20no%20interference%20from%20the%20government.%20There%20is%20no%20room%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Karnataka%20Health%20Minister%20Dinesh%20Gundu%20Rao%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20a%20driver%20identified%20as%20Ravi%2C%20who%20had%20taken%20Renuka%20Swamy%20from%20Chitradurga%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20200%20km%20apart%2C%20surrendered%20before%20the%20police.%20Another%20accused%2C%20Raghu%20alias%20Raghavendra%2C%20had%20along%20with%20others%20arranged%20Ravi's%20taxi%20and%20boarded%20it%20in%20Chitradurga%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi%20went%20into%20hiding%20after%20dropping%20them%20off%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Later%2C%20he%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20taxi%20association%20in%20Chitradurga%2C%20who%20told%20him%20to%20surrender%20to%20the%20police%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghu%20ran%20a%20fan%20club%20of%20the%20Kannada%20actor%20in%20Chitradurga.%20The%20actor%20hired%20him%20to%20gather%20information%20about%20Renuka%20Swamy%2C%20the%20police%20had%20said.%20Renuka%20Swamy's%20wife%20alleged%20he%20was%20kidnapped%20from%20near%20their%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20and%20his%20aides%20dumped%20the%20body%20by%20a%20road.%20A%20food%20delivery%20rider%20saw%20the%20body%20and%20called%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCTV%20footage%20shows%20two%20cars%20-%20one%20of%20them%20linked%20to%20Mr%20Thoogudeepa%20-%20leaving%20the%20area%20after%20dumping%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718359500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%