taken%20into%20Gaza%2C%20as%20hostage.%20Unbeknownst%20to%20Ms%20Argamani%20and%20three%20other%20hostages%20in%20the%20area%2C%20Israeli%20commandos%20had%20infiltrated%20the%20camp%20to%20launch%20a%20daring%20rescue%20operation%20to%20free%20them%2C%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2F06%2F09%2Fisrael-gaza-hostages-rescue-raid%2F%5C%22%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2011%20am%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20rescue%2C%20Israeli%20soldiers%20burst%20into%20the%20apartment%20where%20Ms%20Argamani%20was%20being%20held%2C%20declaring%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20being%20rescued!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rescue%20mission%2C%20which%20also%20freed%20Almog%20Meir%20Jan%2C%2022%2C%20Andrey%20Kozlov%2C%2027%2C%20and%20Shlomi%20Ziv%2C%2041%2C%20was%20marked%20by%20intense%20preparation%20and%20military%20engagement.%20Planned%20for%20weeks%2C%20the%20operation%20involved%20thousands%20of%20troops%2C%20advanced%20technological%20support%2C%20and%20precise%20execution%20the%20report%20says.%20Israeli%20intelligence%2C%20with%20US%20assistance%2C%20%C2%A0analysed%20digital%20data%2C%20drone%20footage%2C%20and%20communications%20intercepts%20to%20locate%20the%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20upon%20confirming%20the%20hostages'%20location%20in%20Nuseirat%2C%20Israeli%20forces%20constructed%20detailed%20mock-ups%20of%20the%20buildings%20to%20rehearse%20the%20rescue.%20According%20to%20the%20report%2C%20this%20preparation%20echoed%20the%20famed%20Operation%20Entebbe%20of%201976%2C%20a%20counter-terrorism%20operation%20in%20Uganda%20initiated%20in%20response%20to%20the%20hijacking%20of%20an%20international%20civilian%20flight%20operated%20by%20Air%20France%20on%20its%20route%20from%20Tel%20Aviv%20to%20Paris.%20Despite%20the%20daylight%20timing%20of%20the%20raid%20posing%20higher%20risks%2C%20Israeli%20military%20strategists%20deemed%20it%20the%20best%20chance%20for%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20break%20of%20morning%2C%20the%20mission%20was%20kicked%20off.%20IDF%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20Herzi%20Halevi%20and%20other%20top%20security%20officials%20monitored%20from%20a%20command%20room.%20Special%20forces%20disguised%20in%20undercover%20vehicles%2C%20including%20a%20truck%20mimicking%20a%20civilian%20commercial%20vehicle%20and%20a%20white%20Mercedes%20loaded%20with%20furniture%2C%20approached%20the%20target%20area.%20Eyewitnesses%20described%20the%20sudden%20eruption%20of%20gunfire%20as%20Israeli%20soldiers%20engaged%20Hamas%20militants%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2F06%2F09%2Fisrael-gaza-hostages-rescue-raid%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20claims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20initial%20success%20in%20rescuing%20Ms%20Argamani%20without%20alerting%20her%20guards%2C%20complications%20arose%20with%20the%20other%20hostages.%20A%20firefight%20broke%20out%2C%20transforming%20the%20covert%20raid%20into%20a%20full-blown%20conflict.%20The%20rescue%2C%20though%20ultimately%20successful%20in%20retrieving%20the%20hostages%2C%20left%20a%20trail%20of%20devastation.%20According%20to%20Gaza%20health%20officials%2C%20over%20270%20Palestinians%20were%20killed%2C%20including%20civilians%20caught%20in%20the%20crossfire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rescued%20hostages%20were%20eventually%20flown%20to%20safety%2C%20with%20the%20mission's%20success%20hailed%20by%20Israeli%20authorities%20despite%20the%20heavy%20price.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20251%20people%20seized%20by%20Hamas%2C%20seven%20captives%20have%20been%20freed%20alive%20by%20Israeli%20forces.%20Currently%2C%20there%20are%20116%20hostages%20still%20in%20Gaza%2C%20including%2041%20whom%20the%20army%20believes%20are%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%2C%20the%20deadliest%20in%20Gaza's%20history%2C%20began%20with%20a%20deadly%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20on%20southern%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20resulting%20in%201%2C189%20Israeli%20deaths%20and%20252%20hostages%20taken.%20Israel's%20response%20has%20been%20relentless%2C%20with%20the%20Gaza%20Health%20Ministry%20reporting%20over%2037%2C232%20deaths%2C%20mostly%20civilians.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718358480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fkp31s5sg_gaza-reuters-_625x300_14_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-israel-commandos-infiltrated-gaza-to-rescue-hostages-in-daring-mission-5888548%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Nuseirat%20refugee%20camp%20is%20located%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20deep%20inside%20Palestinian%20territory.%20It%20was%20in%20one%20of%20the%20camp's%20many%20markets%20that%20Hamas%20had%20kept%20Noa%20Argamani%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20Israeli%20woman%2C%20as%20hostage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-israel-commandos-infiltrated-gaza-to-rescue-hostages-in-daring-mission-5888548%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-israel-commandos-infiltrated-gaza-to-rescue-hostages-in-daring-mission-5888548%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-israel-commandos-infiltrated-gaza-to-rescue-hostages-in-daring-mission-5888548%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Boys%E2%80%99%20Season%204%20Is%20Now%20Streaming%20Online%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718358098000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FTHBY_S4_UT_402_220926_SAVJAS_01022_R1_Crop_3000.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236037797%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CThe%20Boys%E2%80%9D%20are%20back%20in%20town.%20The%20R-rated%20superhero%20series%20returns%20to%20Prime%20Video%20for%2