0Having%20been%20acknowledged%20as%20the%20face%20of%20the%20campaign%20that%20propelled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-results-live-video-congress-worker-hugs-rahul-gandhi-outside-aicc-headquarters-as-party-leads-on-100-seats-5815008%5C%22%3ECongress%20from%2052%20to%2099%20seats%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Rahul%20ought%20to%20have%20promptly%20thanked%20the%20party%20for%20reposing%20faith%20in%20him%20and%20accepted%20the%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20that%20party%20general%20secretary%20K.C.%20Venugopal%2C%20a%20trusted%20aide%20of%20Rahul%2C%20said%20post%20the%20meeting%20was%20that%20after%20having%20heard%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20members%2C%20he%20would%20take%20a%20decision%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELoPs%20In%20The%20Past%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20position%20of%20LoP%20has%20existed%20in%20India's%20parliamentary%20system%20since%20the%20days%20of%20the%20Central%20Legislative%20Assembly%20in%20British%20India.%20Motilal%20Nehru%20held%20that%20position%20in%201923.%20During%20his%20tenure%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20delay%20legislation%2C%20including%20finance%20bills%2C%20of%20the%20Raj.%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi%20never%20held%20the%20position.%20Nehru%20was%20a%20three-term%20Prime%20Minister%3B%20Indira%20Gandhi%20lost%20power%20and%20also%20failed%20to%20get%20elected%20in%201977.%20Thus%2C%20during%20the%20Janata%20Party's%20rule%2C%20Yashwantrao%20Chavan%20and%20C.M.%20Stephen%20functioned%20as%20LoP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20leader%20to%20be%20formally%20recognised%20as%20LoP%2C%20a%20party%20in%20opposition%20requires%20a%20minimum%20of%2010%25%20of%20the%20total%20strength%20of%20the%20House.%20Until%20the%20Congress%20split%20in%201969%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20had%20no%20LoP.%20Ram%20Subhag%20Singh%20of%20the%20Congress%20(O)%20was%20accorded%20this%20recognition%20in%201969%20when%20more%20than%2010%25%20of%20MPs%20joined%20the%20exodus%20against%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20However%2C%20the%20privilege%20of%20an%20LoP%20getting%20the%20status%20and%20facilities%20of%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20had%20to%20wait%20until%201977%2C%20when%20the%20Janata%20regime%20of%20Morarji%20Desai%20amended%20the%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-man-of-match-should-be-leader-of-opposition-shashi-tharoor-5838913%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Rahul%20Gandhi%20'Man%20Of%20The%20Match'%2C%20Should%20Be%20Leader%20Of%20Opposition%3A%20Shashi%20Tharoor%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20Gandhi%20was%20LoP%20in%201989-90%3B%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20(BJP)%20L.K.%20Advani%20and%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20took%20turns%20as%20LoP%20between%201990%20and%201996.%20P.V.%20Narasimha%20Rao%20served%20in%20that%20position%20for%20a%20fortnight%20during%20Vajpayee's%20short-lived%20premiership.%20Sharad%20Pawar%20was%20the%20Congress%20party's%20LoP%20for%20just%20over%20a%20year%20in%201998%20before%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20took%20over%20the%20party's%20reins%20and%20also%20became%20LoP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20(1999-2004).%20During%20the%20decade%20of%20Congress-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20rule%20(2004-2014)%2C%20L.K.%20Advani%20and%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20were%20the%20LoPs%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20Eyes%20On%20Rahul%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20as%20no%20party%20has%20had%20a%2010%25%20share%20-%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20got%2044%20seats%20in%202014%20and%2052%20in%202019%20-%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Parliament%20in%202014%20(Mallikarjun%20Kharge)%20and%202019%20(Adhir%20Ranjan%20Choudhury)%20were%20not%20accorded%20LoP%20status.%20However%2C%20for%20purposes%20of%20selecting%20key%20government%20positions%2C%20where%20the%20statute%20requires%20consultation%20with%20LoP%2C%20they%20were%20invited%20to%20selection%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Congress%20bouncing%20back%20with%2099%20seats%20(the%20strength%20has%20since%20grown%20to%20101%20with%20two%20independents%2C%20both%20Congress%20members%20before%20polls%2C%20joining%20the%20Congress%20in%20Parliament)%2C%20the%20decade-long%20'banishment'%20is%20now%20over%2C%20and%20the%20party%20is%20looking%20towards%20Rahul%20to%20be%20its%20face%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerformance%20As%20An%20MP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Rahul%20accepts%20the%20job%2C%20it%20will%20require%20his%20presence%20in%20Parliament%20for%20most%20days%20of%20a%20session.%20His%20attendance%20as%20an%20MP%2C%20both%20from%20Amethi%20and%20Wayanad%2C%20between%202004-2019%2C%20has%20not%20been%20too%20encouraging.%20He%20went%20on%20sojourns%20abroad%20when%20Parliament%20was%20in%20session%2C%20and%20his%20record%20in%20asking%20questions%20and%20participating%20in%20debates%20has%20been%20dismal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20campaign%2C%20Rahul%20boasted%20about%20his%20knowledge%20of%20the%20government%20system%20as%20an%20insider%20for%20years.%20The%20real%20test%20awaits%20him%20now%3A%20to%20provide%20effective%20leadership%20to%20the%20232%20INDIA%20bloc%20MPs%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Narendra%20Modi%20heads%20a%20coalition%20of%20293-member%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-wayanad-raebareli-question-rahul-gandhis-both-will-be-happy-remark-5876846%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0On%20Wayanad-Raebareli%20Question%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3BBoth%20Will%20Be%20Happy%26quot%3B%20Remark%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20worthwhile%20to%20recall%20a%20note%20in%20the%20diary%20maintained%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20de%20facto%20number%20two%20in%20her%20last%20dispensation%20as%20Prime%20Minister.%20The%20views%20of%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%2C%20who%20became%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20have%20been%20recorded%20in%20Sharmishtha%20Mukherjee's%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EPranab%2C%20My%20Father%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BHe%20%5BRahul%5D%20has%20all%20the%20arrogance%20of%20his%20Nehru-Gandhi%20lineage%20without%20their%20political%20acumen...Maybe%20politics%20isn't%20his%20calling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20LoP%2C%20Rahul%20will%20have%20to%20follow%20rules%20and%20procedures.%20Frequent%20absences%20from%20House%20proceedings%20will%20not%20go%20down%20well.%20LoP%20has%20to%20be%20cautious%20and%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Sonia%20Question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%20dilemma%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20facing%20another%20crunch%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20After%20Sonia%20became%20the%20party%20President%20in%201998%2C%20the%20Congress%20constitution%20was%20amended%20to%20provide%20that%20the%20party%20chief%20shall%20be%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Parliament%2C%20even%20if%20he%20or%20she%20is%20not%20an%20MP.%20Sonia's%20election%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%201999%20saw%20her%20occupying%20both%20posts%20for%20over%20two%20decades.%20Though%20she%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20Congress%20President%20or%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20being%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20she%20has%20now%20been%20re-elected%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsonia-gandhi-re-elected-as-congress-parliamentary-party-chairperson-5846946%5C%22%3Echairperson%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Parliament%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Thus%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20the%20party%20chief%2C%20will%20be%20the%20LoP%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20with%20Sonia%20adorning%20the%20front%20benches%20of%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20indeed%20becomes%20the%20LoP%2C%20he%20may%20like%20to%20carry%20forward%20the%20parliamentary%20legacy%20of%20Feroze%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20original%20Rae%20Bareli%20MP%20(1952%2C%201957)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20dust%20the%20records%20of%20his%20great-great-grandfather%2C%20Motilal%20Nehru%2C%20who%20as%20the%20LoP%20could%20stall%20and%20delay%20legislation%20of%20the%20British%20Raj%20in%201923.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParliament%20of%20India's%20first%20successful%20scam-busting%20was%20done%20by%20Feroze%20Gandhi%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20resignation%20of%20the%20then-finance%20minister%20in%20February%201958.%20The%20then%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20could%20not%20find%20fault%20with%20Feroze%20Gandhi's%20well-researched%2C%20articulated%20diatribe%2C%20which%20was%20carried%20out%20as%20per%20parliamentary%20rules%20and%20procedure.%20Precedents%20set%20in%20that%20debate%20endure%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20Speaker's%20rulings%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20has%20turned%20the%20fortunes%20of%20his%20party%20and%20nipped%20the%20talk%20of%20a%20'Congress-%3Cem%3Emukt%20%3C%2Fem%3EBharat'%2C%20measure%20up%20to%20the%20expectations%20expressed%20in%20the%20CWC's%20resolution%3F%20Or%20will%20he%20choose%20to%20shun%20responsibility%20once%20again%20-%20just%20as%20he%20had%20winked%20at%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20offer%2C%20supported%20by%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%20during%20the%20UPA%20regime%2C%20that%20he%20become%20a%20minister%20and%20gain%20administrative%20experience%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20Editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718356920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F718j3mb8_rahul-gandhi-yatra_120x90_28_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcongresss-new-dilemma-will-rahul-agree-to-be-leader-of-opposition-5888631%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Will%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20has%20turned%20the%20fortun