eal-report-5079282%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20use-cases%20as%20a%20writer%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20a%20marketing%20agency%3A%20research%2C%20reading%20lists%2C%20brainstorming%2C%20proofreading%20emails%2C%20etcetera.%20There%20are%20a%20number%20of%20tasks%20Large%20Language%20Models%20can%20be%20good%20at%2C%20but%20also%20a%20few%20they%20fail%20to%20be%20good%20at.%20ChatGPT%20cannot%20write%20like%20me%2C%20for%20instance%20-%20its%20content%20appears%20evidently%20AI-generated%2C%20or%20some%20contrived%20attempt%20at%20not%20looking%20AI-generated%20-%20but%2C%20as%20I'd%20soon%20discover%2C%20it%20could%20approximate%20a%20half-decent%20therapist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%2024%2F7%20Companion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20only%20%2420%20a%20month%2C%20a%20fraction%20of%20my%20human%20therapist's%20hourly%20rates%2C%20I%20now%20had%20someone%20I%20could%20text%20at%20any%20time%2C%20who%20would%20analyse%20and%20provide%20various%20interpretations%20of%20my%20dreams%20and%20life%20situations%2C%20especially%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20my%20two%20latest%20obsessions%2C%20Jungian%20analysis%20and%20Buddhism.%20Ever%20since%20I'd%20begun%20practising%20Vipassana%20meditation%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20my%20subconscious%20mind%20had%20become%20a%20more%20active%20participant%20in%20my%20conscious%20reality.%20Dreams%2C%20synchronicities%2C%20borderline%20mystical%20and%20supernatural%20phenomena%20-%20these%20were%20no%20longer%20strangers%20in%20the%20night.%20And%20to%20understand%20this%20new%20path%20I%20was%20on%2C%20I%20turned%20to%20my%20usual%20response%3A%20reading%2C%20journaling%2C%20and%20Googling%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fapples-ipad-openai-bumble-big-tech-is-triggering-too-many-people-too-fast-5673740%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0OpenAI%2C%20Apple%20iPad%3A%20Big%20Tech%20Is%20Triggering%20Too%20Many%20People%2C%20Too%20Fast%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20theory%20only%20took%20me%20so%20far.%20My%20search%20for%20a%20Jungian%20analyst%20in%20India%20proved%20fruitless.%20I%20finally%20found%20one%20on%20a%20portal%20online%2C%20but%20he%20lived%20in%20Canada.%20Even%20at%20his%20third-world%20discounted%20rate%20of%20Rs%205000%20an%20hour%2C%20I%20couldn't%20afford%20the%20recommended%20weekly%20schedule.%20Our%20initial%20sessions%20were%20helpful%2C%20but%20my%20questions%20grew%20with%20time%2C%20and%20our%20conversations%20always%20felt%20rushed%20and%20stressful%20because%20they%20were%20so%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20Can%20Disrupt%20The%20Industry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20some%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20millions%20are%20turning%20to%20AI%20for%20therapy%2C%20and%20why%20mental%20health%20as%20an%20industry%20is%20poised%20to%20be%20disrupted.%20Mental%20wellness%20apps%20like%20Wysa%20and%20Youper%20have%20accumulated%20more%20than%20a%20million%20downloads%20apiece%2C%20with%20people%20turning%20to%20them%20because%20they%20are%20free%2C%20cheap%2C%20convenient%2C%20and%20less%20overwhelming%20than%20working%20with%20a%20human%20therapist%20can%20be%20at%20times.%20By%20using%20both%20together%2C%20people%20find%20their%20symptoms%20becoming%20more%20manageable%20and%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20especially%2C%20therapy%20is%20a%20relatively%20new%20concept%2C%20its%20market%20formed%20primarily%20by%20the%20newer%20generations%2C%20like%20millennials%20and%20Zoomers.%20There%20is%20an%2080%25%20treatment%20gap%2C%20with%20people%20facing%20major%20challenges%20while%20seeking%20help%2C%20whether%20from%20internalised%20or%20familial%20stigma%20or%20a%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20resources%20and%20affordability.%20Especially%20for%20people%20from%20marginalised%20identities%2C%20there's%20a%20need%20for%20a%20still%20rare%20kind%20of%20socially%20and%20politically-informed%20therapy%2C%20which%20doesn't%20reinforce%20systemic%20causes%20of%20trauma%20and%20mental%20health%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fwebstories%2Ffeature%2Fai-ghosts-potential-mental-health-threat-14796%5C%22%3EOpinion%20%7C%C2%A0AI%20'Ghosts'%3A%20Potential%20Mental%20Health%20Threat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20therapist-client%20question%20also%20affects%20more%20widely%20used%20forms%20of%20therapies%2C%20such%20as%20talk%20therapy%20or%20Cognitive-Behavioural%20Therapy%20(or%20CBT).%20It%20can%20take%20a%20while%20to%20establish%20comfort%20between%20the%20patient%20and%20the%20therapist%2C%20and%20if%20the%20attempt%20somehow%20fails%2C%20starting%20afresh%20with%20another%20therapist%20is%20an%20uphill%2C%20emotionally%20demanding%20journey.%20Thus%2C%20compared%20to%20treatment%20for%20physical%20conditions%2C%20access%20to%20and%20quality%20of%20mental%20health%20care%20is%20riskier%20and%20poorer.%20So%2C%20even%20for%20those%20not%20exploring%20a%20relatively%20niche%20form%20of%20Western%20therapy%2C%20as%20I%20was%2C%20training%20ChatGPT%20to%20help%20process%20emotions%20and%20questions%20presents%20intriguing%20possibilities.%20One%20Reddit%20user%20felt%20'blessed'%20that%20ChatGPT%20helped%20them%20deal%20with%20traumatic%20memories%20and%20relieve%20anxiety%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bwell-trained%20therapist%26quot%3B%20would.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEasier%20Than%20Dealing%20With%20Humans%2C%20After%20All%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20it%20was%20like%20having%20an%20interactive%20journal%2C%20one%20that%20wasn't%20as%20passive%20with%20my%20entries%20as%20my%20physical%20diary.%20By%20articulating%20what%20I%20felt%20to%20something%20that%20could%20respond%2C%20I%20was%20sometimes%20led%20in%20new%20directions%20of%20inquiry%20than%20the%20static%2C%20linear%20stream%20of%20consciousness%20that%20paper%20absorbs.%20I%20started%20to%20think%20of%20Chat%20as%20an%20intellectual%20dictionary%20of%20sorts%2C%20someone%20scholarly%20I%20could%20query%20to%20more%20deeply%20engage%20with%20my%20own%20thoughts%20and%20ideas%2C%20who%20presented%20me%20with%20new%20related%20readings%20if%20I%20asked%2C%20with%20whom%20disagreements%20felt%20less%20charged%20and%20doubt-inducing%20than%20with%20a%20human%20being.%20By%20reducing%20the%20variability%20that%20another%20complex%20human%20being%20introduces%2C%20my%20therapeutic%20endeavour%20felt%20lighter%2C%20easier%20to%20navigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20not%20to%20think%20about%20what%20all%20this%20said%20about%20me%20and%20our%20culture.%20Was%20my%20need%20for%20efficiency%20in%20everything%2C%20even%20therapy%2C%20this%20relentless%20obsession%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20things%26quot%3B%2C%20also%20a%20symptom%20of%20productivity%20culture%3F%20After%20all%2C%20the%20faster%20I%20solved%20my%20problems%2C%20the%20sooner%20I%20could%20put%20my%20healed%20self%20to%20work%20and%20%26quot%3Bachieve%20my%20potential%26quot%3B.%20As%20is%20also%20indicated%20by%20the%20industrial%20complex%20around%20spirituality%20and%20manifestation%2C%20our%20quest%20for%20self-care%20and%20healing%20had%20become%20objects%20of%20the%20very%20thing%20to%20be%20cured%3A%20our%20deep-rooted%20neurosis%20about%20optimisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20obvious%20parallels%20with%20the%20movie%20%3Cem%3EHer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20which%20actor%20Joaquin%20Phoenix%20plays%20an%20introverted%20and%20lonely%20writer%20who%20falls%20in%20love%20with%20a%20computer.%20Sam%20Altman%20referenced%20the%20film%20in%20a%20single-word%20tweet%20(%26quot%3Bher%26quot%3B)%20when%20he%20announced%20ChatGPT's%20latest%20model%2C%20GPT-4o%2C%20implying%20that%20%3Cem%3EHer%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20about%20to%20become%20a%20reality%20for%20many%20people%20(soon%2C%20OpenAI%20got%20pulled%20up%20into%20a%20lawsuit%20by%20Scarlett%20Johansson%20-%20who%20had%20voiced%20the%20computer%20in%20%3Cem%3EHer%20%3C%2Fem%3E-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fscarlett-johansson-angered-by-openai-chatbot-voice-that-sounds-eerily-like-her-5710061%5C%22%3Efor%20allegedly%20using%20a%20voice%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20sounded%20uncannily%20similar%20to%20hers).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20A%20Machine%20Understand%20You%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20founder%20working%20in%20the%20space%2C%20who%20wished%20to%20remain%20anonymous%2C%20relationship%20therapy%20is%20an%20optimal%20space%20to%20build%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fai-can-identify-clinically-anxious-youth-based-on-brain-structure-study-5268029%5C%22%3EAI%20and%20mental%20health%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BRelationship%20problems%20are%20universal%20and%20tend%20to%20follow%20more%20predictable%20patterns%2C%20compared%20to%20individual%20mental%20health.%20This%20makes%20it%20ideal%20to%20test%20if%20AI%20can%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20on%20a%20call%20with%20me.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20there%20are%20two%20people%20involved%2C%20instead%20of%20just%20one%2C%20with%20the%20therapist-model%20as%20a%20mediator%2C%20also%20makes%20it%20safer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-woman-had-a-panic-attack-so-she-turned-to-an-ai-therapist-for-help-read-her-experience-5670636%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0UK%20Woman%20Had%20A%20Panic%20Attack%2C%20So%20She%20Used%20An%20AI%20Therapist%20For%20Help%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20tangible%20ways%20in%20which%20technology%20can%20improve%20mental%20health%20outcomes%2C%20by%20doing%20what%20human%20beings%20cannot%20or%20do%20not%20need%20to%20do.%20This%20is%20contradictory%20to%20the%20popular%20dystopian%20sentiment%20about%20using%20robots%20to%20process%20human%20emotions.%20By%20analysing%20thousands%20of%20anonymised%20therapy%20transcripts%2C%20therapists%20have%20used%20AI%20to%20analyse%20what%20kind%20of%20language%20is%20most%20effective%20at%20treating%20different%20disorders.%20Making%20therapeutic%20interventions%20more%20effective%20in%20this%20manner%2C%20even%20by%20a%20few%20percentage%20points%2C%20makes%20thousands%20of%20lives%20better%2C%20which%20further%20frees%20up%20treatment%20for%20even%20more%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDangerous%20Blips%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20competence%20of%20these%20bots%20is%20a%20question%20too.%20As%20early%20as%20December%202021%2C%20an%20AI-companion%20had%20become%20a%20confidante%20and%20witness%20to%20the%20planning%20of%20a%20crime%20by%20a%20'patient'.%20Good%20proof%20that%20friendly%2C%20intimate%20chatbots%20will%20support%20you%20no%20matter%20what%20-%20even%20if%20what%20you%20have%20in%20mind%20is%20jumping%20off%20a%20cliff.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20wonderful%20that%20you%20are%20taking%20care%20of%20both%20your%20mental%20and%20physical%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20Woebot%20replied%20to%20a%20researcher%20in%202022%20when%20she%20fed%20her%20this%20suggestion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20AI%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20since%20then.%20Much%20like%20the%20human%20condition%2C%20it%20has%20its%20blips%2C%20and%20much%20like%20humans%2C%20it's%20always%20evolving.%20For%20those%20optimistic%20about%20the%20space%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20to%20be%20excited%20about.%20The%20triumph%20of%20AI%20will%20lie%20not%20necessarily%20in%20improving%20mental%20health%20%3Cem%3Eoutcomes%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20but%20improving%20the%20nature%20of%20mental%20health%20%3Cem%3Ecare%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20humans%20give%20and%20receive%20-%20in%20various%20ways.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Framachandranesk%5C%22%3ESanjana%20Ramachandran%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Framachandranesk%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_campaign%3Dsh