ities%20in%20their%20data%20through%20their%20responsible%20disclosure%20programme%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20343%20million%20people%20have%20been%20the%20victims%20of%20cyber%20attacks%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Forbes%20report.%20Data%20breaches%20also%20saw%20a%2072%20percent%20increase%20in%202023%20compared%20to%202021%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20need%20for%20ethical%20hackers%20and%20cyber%20security%20experts%20all%20the%20more%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Class%2012%2C%20Muneeb%20pursued%20a%20B.Tech%20in%20Computer%20Science%20in%20a%20college%20which%20was%2080%20km%20away.%20The%20daily%20travel%20and%20classes%20left%20him%20with%20no%20time%20to%20pursue%20his%20passion.%20Supported%20by%20his%20father%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20drop%20out%20in%20the%20second%20year%20to%20focus%20entirely%20on%20ethical%20hacking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20either%20complete%20my%20engineering%20degree%20or%20focus%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F231525%2Fcyfirma-startup-cybersecurity-chinese-hackers-india-cert-malware-phishing-dark-web-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecybersecurity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20follow%20my%20passion%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20a%20BCA%20degree%20in%20cyber%20security%20which%20also%20allowed%20me%20the%20time%20to%20hone%20my%20skills%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2022-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20now%20pursuing%20BCA%20through%20correspondence%20from%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20National%20Open%20University%20(IGNOU).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-21-1717502240.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Muneeb%20Amin%20Bhat%20with%20his%20setup%20at%20home%5C%22%20srcs