ed%20for%20that.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20used%20to%20hate%20travelling%20to%20work%20while%20wearing%20a%20pad%20in%20the%20heat%20but%20now%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20any%20discomfort%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Asan%20continuously%20reaches%20women%20in%20rural%20India%2C%20Ira%20believes%20that%20her%20work%20is%20not%20over.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20still%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20women%20using%20rags%20and%20lacking%20any%20access%20to%20menstrual%20hygiene.%20If%20even%20one%20woman%20is%20without%20access%20to%20menstrual%20hygiene%2C%20my%20job%20is%20not%20over.%20As%20a%20company%2C%20we%20want%20to%20eradicate%20period%20poverty%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20pictures%20credit%3A%20Ira%20Guha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717079206000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-1-1717078112.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351606%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20cups%20come%20with%20a%20cloth%20bag%20and%20a%20instruction%20manual%20in%20the%20local%20language.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351606%2Fmenstrual-cups-made-in-india-asan-cup-how-to-use-ira-guha-period-hygiene-for-rural-women-karnataka%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Organic%20Tea%20Tasting%20%26amp%3B%20Waterfall%20Picnics%3A%20Eco-Stay%20in%20Coonoor%20Is%20a%20Nature%20Lover%E2%80%99s%20Dream%20Destination%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20eve%20of%20her%2010th%20birthday%2C%20Mahima%20Sukhdev%E2%80%99s%20parents%20Vinati%20and%20Pavan%20posed%20a%20very%20important%20question%20to%20her%3A%20How%20would%20you%20like%20to%20celebrate%3F%20They%20had%20imagined%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20coloured%20responses%20%E2%80%94%20think%20al